ttps://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/S%C6%A1n-th%C3%B4n-c%E1%BA%A3m-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-v6_CQ6TsQFBYRt0-vHeBmA">Sơn thôn cảm hứng - 山村感興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/Th%E1%BB%89nh-ho%C3%A0n-V%E1%BA%ADt-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%ADt-%C3%81c-nh%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-6ORZQReq0kHk4HzgN3B8ow">Thỉnh hoàn Vật Dương, Vật Ác nhị động biểu - 請還勿陽，勿惡二峒表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-sMXrZTDvW5uflSvv6NTMXQ">Lý Nhân Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%E1%BB%AB-Ch%C3%A2u-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung/poem-D-bWpjLle9k2lqrysB28kA">Từ Châu đạo trung - 徐州道中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
